bras-cu-agent_schema.description: Specify configuration information of CU agent.

cu-agent.description: Enable/disable the UP mode so that the current device functions as a vBRAS-UP.

interface-monitoring-groups.description: List of configuring a vBRAS-UP to track the session status of interface monitoring groups to detect network-side link faults.

interface-monitoring-group.description: Configure a vBRAS-UP to track the session status of a specified interface monitoring group.

name.description: Name of an interface monitoring group.

down-weight.description: Interface weight for reporting a network-side fault. A higher weight indicates a higher fault priority.

route-monitoring-groups.description: List of configuring a vBRAS-UP to track the session status of a route monitoring group to detect network-side link faults.

route-monitoring-group.description: Configure a vBRAS-UP to track the session status of a specified route monitoring group.

name.description: Name of a route monitoring group.

down-weight.description: Route weight for reporting a network-side fault. A higher weight indicates a higher fault priority.

bfd-sessions.description: List of configure a vBRAS-UP to track the status of a BFD session to detect access-side faults.

bfd-session.description: Configure a vBRAS-UP to track the status of a BFD session.

up-nqa-detect.description: Enable/disable NQA dectct to the VXLAN tunnel.

count.description: Number of sent Echo Request messages.

interval.description: Time elapses before a next Echo Request message is sent.

timeout.description: Timeout period of waiting for an Echo Reply message.

up-cusp-agent.description: Operational state of binding a CUSP agent to the vBRAS-UP and the control tunnel between the vBRAS-CP and vBRAS-UP is established.

name.description: Name of the CUSP agent bound to the control tunnel. After the CUSP agent is bound to the vBRAS-UP, the control tunnel between the vBRAS-CP and vBRAS-UP is established.

up-vxlan-channels.description: List of binding VxLAN Tunnel state.

up-versions.description: List of Checking CU interface version information on the UP side state.

up-version.description: Checking CU interface version information on the UP side state.
